{"word":"οἰνοθήρας","slug":"οἰνοθήρας","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n72508\" key=\"oi)noqh/ras\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">οἰνο-θήρας</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ου</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>, a plant <sense id=\"n72508.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the root of which smells of wine</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">was used to flavour wine</tr_> ; but in the best Mss. of <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0093.tlg001:9:19:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Thphr.\">Thphr.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HP\">HP</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.19.1</biblScope> </bibl> it is <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὀνοθήρας,</foreign> as in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Dsc.\">Dsc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.117</biblScope> </bibl> and <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Gal.\">Gal.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12.89</biblScope> </bibl> ; called also <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὀνάγρα</orth>, Gal.l.c., and <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὀνόθουρις</orth> ibid., <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0718.tlg015:15\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aët.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.15</biblScope> </bibl> ; cf. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">onothuris,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:latinLit:phi0978.phi001:24:167\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Plin.\">Plin.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">HN</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24.167</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}